Things to Avoid while learning Selenium


	1. Do not aim becoming a Selenium expert / genius in 2 or 3 months it will take time

	-- Learn in 2/3  months Selenium and get a job in a good company.


	2. No Use of Selenium WebDriver Certifications.
	

	3.Jumping into selenium without programming.
	

	4.Look for Selenium Books, Online Courses.


	5.Do not Learn Selenium IDE and Selenium RC.


	6.Learn by yourself only
 	Set the different small milestones - but share with others.
 	
 
	